snippet.title: ONE MILLION People Want Amber Heard FIRED Off Aquaman 2?!
snippet.description:
A petition addressed to Warner Bros. to fire Amber Heard off 'Aquaman 2' has reached well over a million signatures. Depp, meanwhile, has been fired off Fantastic Beasts 3... but the studio still has to pay him his FULL salary. But could Amber Heard actually have a BIGGER role as Mera in the sequel?
